snippet.title: The Wild At Heart gamescom 2020 Trailer
snippet.description:
Venture forth in 2021 with Wake and Kirby in The Wild at Heart. 

A coming of age tale about how two friends embark on a journey that will test their strength, heart, and wits to restore an ancient society before it fades forever.
